Haɗakar yawan kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) cikin sauri a cikin Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya, daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020
Adadin masu kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) yana nuna irin wannan yanayin a cikin Tarayyar Turai / ƙasashen Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya, wanda ke tabbatar da cewa, yayin da a wani mataki daban dangane da ƙasar, annobar COVID-19 tana ci gaba cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Dangane da kwarewar Italiya, ƙasashe, asibitoci da rukunin kulawa mai mahimmanci ya kamata su haɓaka shirye-shiryen su don ƙaruwar marasa lafiya tare da COVID-19 waɗanda zasu buƙaci kulawar lafiya, musamman kulawa mai mahimmanci.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an ba da rahoton tarin cututtukan ciwon huhu na rashin sananne a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cutar Sin ta ba da rahoton cewa mai haifar da cutar sabon coronavirus ne wanda yanzu ake kira da cutar coronavirus 2 mai tsanani mai saurin numfashi (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da ke haifar da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 an kira ta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Shaida har zuwa yau ita ce kusan kashi 80% na mutanen da ke da COVID-19 suna da rashin lafiya, watau kamuwa da cuta ta hanyar numfashi tare da ko ba tare da ciwon huhu ba, kuma yawancin waɗannan suna murmurewa.
A cikin kusan kashi 14 cikin ɗari, COVID-19 yana ci gaba zuwa wata cuta mai tsanani da ke buƙatar asibiti yayin da sauran kashi 6 cikin ɗari ke fuskantar mummunan cuta da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Mutuwar marasa lafiya da aka kwantar a asibiti saboda COVID-19 kusan 4%.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun kimanta yanayin tarin kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EU/EEA) da kuma Burtaniya (UK) kuma mun kwatanta su da na lardin Hubei, China.
Mun kuma kwatanta adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a yanzu a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya da na Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
Al'amuran COVID-19 a ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya ci gaba da yaduwar yanki kuma yanayin annobar COVID-19 a sauran duniya a halin yanzu ya bi na wannan ƙasar.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin fitowar 5 ga Maris na Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri da sauransu sun ba da rahoton farkon mutanen Turai da aka tabbatar da cutar COVID-19 bisa ga ma'anar yanayin WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, Faransa ta ba da rahoton farkon mutane uku da aka tabbatar da su a ranar 24 ga Janairu 2020 a cikin mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris 2020, an gano shari'o'in COVID-19 a duk ƙasashe 30 na EU / EEA da United Kingdom (UK), inda tsakanin 31 ga Disamba 2019 da wannan kwanan wata, an ba da rahoton shari'o'i 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727, tare da shari'o'i 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 a Italiya kadai.
Samun adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 da kuma yawan kamuwa da su
A Cibiyar Tsaro da Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), ana sabunta adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 da aka sanar a kowace kasa a duniya, wanda aka samu ne kawai daga tushen hukuma kamar ma'aikatar lafiya ta ƙasashen, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki da WHO, kowace rana da karfe 8:00 na safe.
An yi amfani da waɗannan bayanan don kimanta yanayin COVID-19 a EU / EEA da Burtaniya, da kuma kwatanta su da na Italiya.
A matsayin wakilcin yaduwar masu cutar COVID-19, mun lissafta adadin adadin masu cutar COVID-19 na kwanaki 14, ta haka ne la'akari da yanayin COVID-19, a kowace ƙasa ta EU / EEA da Burtaniya, a lokacin 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
Mun kuma gabatar da adadin adadin masu kamuwa da cutar da aka sanar a kowace kasa a ranar 15 ga Maris 2020 da karfe 8:00 na safe idan aka kwatanta da na Italiya a tsawon 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya
Yanayin a cikin kwanaki 14 na tarin adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU / EEA da Burtaniya gabaɗaya sun bi na lardin Hubei (China) (Hoto 1).
Ga EU/EEA da Burtaniya gabaɗaya, tarawar cutar COVID-19 ta fara ƙaruwa a kusa da 21 ga Fabrairu sannan ta ƙaru sosai a kusa da 28 ga Fabrairu 2020 (Karin bayani).
Wannan ya kasance galibi saboda saurin karuwar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar daga Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen EU / EEA da Burtaniya sun nuna irin wannan yanayin karuwar tarin cutar ta COVID-19 (Karin bayani).
Shafi na 2 ya nuna adadin adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19, a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya idan aka kwatanta da na Italiya a cikin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
Ya nuna cewa a ranar 15 ga Maris da karfe 8:00 na safe, wasu ƙasashe 15 na EU/EEA da Burtaniya sun riga sun ba da rahoton jimillar adadin masu cutar da za a iya kwatanta su da na Italiya makonni 3 da suka gabata ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin waɗanda aka sanar da su na COVID-19 yana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a EU / EEA da Burtaniya.
Yanayin da aka lura a cikin tarin kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 ya nuna cewa annobar tana ci gaba da irin wannan saurin a dukkan ƙasashe.
Wannan duk da cewa ƙasashe suna cikin matakai daban-daban, bambance-bambance a cikin martani na lafiyar jama'a na ƙasa, kuma mai yiwuwa ma'anoni daban-daban a cikin ƙasashe da ladabi daban-daban don zaɓar marasa lafiya waɗanda dole ne a gwada su don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da gwajin kamawa.
A farkon Maris 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta shafa na Italiya sun bayyana halin da ake ciki wanda kusan kashi 10% na marasa lafiya da ke da COVID-19 ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ba da rahoton cewa asibitoci da rukunin kulawa mai tsanani a waɗannan yankuna sun riga sun kai iyakar ƙarfin su.
Bayanai kan shigar da masu cutar COVID-19 a asibiti da/ko sashen kulawa mai tsanani a halin yanzu ana samun su a matakin EU/EEA ne kawai na kashi 6% da 1% na masu cutar, bi da bi (ba a nuna bayanai ba).
Duk da haka, ya kamata a tattara su ta hanyar da ta dace don a kara wa bayanan sa ido na yanzu da suka maida hankali kan adadin wadanda aka ruwaito da kuma adadin mutuwar.
Wani bincike da aka gudanar a 201011 ya nuna bambancin da ke tsakanin samun gadajen kulawa mai tsanani da na kulawa ta tsakiya a Turai, daga 29.2 a Jamus zuwa 4.2 gadaje ga kowane mutum 100,000 a Portugal.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe na iya samun ƙarin ko ƙasa da albarkatu fiye da Italiya (12,5 gadajen kulawa mai zurfi da kulawa ta tsakiya a kowace mutane 100,000 a 201011).
An bayar da yanayin ƙira da ya shafi wadatar ƙarfin kiwon lafiya, tare da kimantawa ga kowace ƙasar EU / EEA da Burtaniya na yawan waɗanda ke cikin asibiti na COVID-19 da ke da alaƙa da &gt; 90% haɗarin wucewar ƙarfin gado mai kulawa mai mahimmanci a cikin sabuntawa ta shida na ECDC mai saurin kimanta haɗarin COVID-19.
Tunda har zuwa yanzu an tattara masu kamuwa da cutar a wasu yankuna a cikin kasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya, kuma asibitoci da rukunin kulawa mai mahimmanci galibi suna ba da sabis ga ƙididdigar ƙididdigar yankin yankin, ya kamata a samar da bayanai game da masu kamuwa da cuta da gadajen kulawa mai mahimmanci a matakin Nomenclature of territorial units for statistics 2 (NUTS-2).
Kwarewar Italiya da yanayin da ake ciki a yanzu a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 tana ci gaba cikin sauri a EU / EEA da Burtaniya.
Kasashe, asibitoci da rukunin kulawa mai mahimmanci ya kamata su shirya kansu don yanayin ci gaba da watsa SARS-CoV-2 a cikin al'umma da haɓaka yawan marasa lafiya tare da COVID-19 waɗanda ke buƙatar kulawa ta lafiya, musamman kulawa mai mahimmanci, kamar wanda ke faruwa a yankunan da cutar ta shafa na Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin rahoton ECDC na kwanan nan, hanzarin tantance hadarin, hanzarin, da kuma cikakkiyar hanya yana da mahimmanci don jinkirta yaduwar SARS-COV-2, tare da sauyawa daga hanawa zuwa hanyar ragewa, saboda saurin karuwar da ake tsammani a cikin adadin shari'o'in na iya ba masu yanke shawara da asibitoci isasshen lokaci don fahimta, karɓa da daidaita martani daidai idan ba a aiwatar da su ba a gaba.
Binciken hadarin cikin sauri ya kuma lissafa matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a don rage tasirin annobar.
Akwai ɗan gajeren lokacin da ƙasashe ke da damar ƙara ƙoƙarin sarrafawa don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da rage matsin lamba kan kiwon lafiya.
Idan ba haka ba, yana yiwuwa tsarin kiwon lafiya na sauran ƙasashen EU / EEA zai fuskanci hauhawar marasa lafiya waɗanda ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Barkewar cutar Coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wadda cutar coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) ta haifar, ta kashe mutane sama da 3,000 kuma ta kamu da mutane sama da 80,000 a China da sauran wurare a duniya, wanda hakan ya haifar da bala'i ga mutane.
Kamar kwayar cutarta ta homologous, SARS-CoV, wanda ya haifar da SARS a dubban mutane a 2003, SARS-CoV-2 kuma ana iya watsa shi daga bat kuma yana haifar da irin wannan bayyanar ta hanyar irin wannan tsari.
Koyaya, COVID-19 yana da ƙarancin tsanani da mutuwar fiye da SARS amma yana da yaduwa sosai kuma yana shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa da maza fiye da mata.
A amsa ga yawan littattafan da ke ƙaruwa da sauri game da cutar da ke tasowa, wannan labarin yana ƙoƙari ya ba da cikakken nazari game da batun bincike mai saurin tasowa.
Za mu rufe abubuwan da suka shafi ilimin cututtuka, ilimin cututtuka, ilimin kwayar cuta, ganewar asali, magani, tsinkaya, da rigakafin cutar.
Ko da yake tambayoyi da yawa suna bukatar amsa, muna fatan cewa wannan bita zai taimaka wajen fahimtar da kuma kawar da wannan cuta mai barazana.
Bikin bazara a ranar 25 ga Janairu, 2020 ya zama abin tunawa da ba a taba gani ba ga duk Sinawa wadanda aka bukaci su zauna a gida a duk lokacin hutu da kuma makonni da yawa bayan haka saboda barkewar sabuwar cutar kwayar cuta.
Kwayar cutar tana da kamanceceniya sosai da kwayar cutar coronavirus (CoV) wacce ta haifar da barkewar cutar mai saurin numfashi (SARS) a 2003; saboda haka, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta sanya mata sunan SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, kuma cutar da ke da alaƙa da ita an sanya mata sunan CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Annobar ta fara ne a Wuhan, China, kuma da sauri ta bazu a duk faɗin ƙasar da kusan wasu 50 a duk faɗin duniya.
Ya zuwa ranar 2 ga Maris, 2020, kwayar cutar ta haifar da sama da 80,000 da aka tabbatar da cutar ta COVID-19, tare da sama da marasa lafiya 40,000 da aka sallama kuma sama da marasa lafiya 3,000 da suka mutu.
WHO ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 shine abokin gaba na 1 kuma mai yuwuwar zama mafi iko fiye da ta'addanci.
A cewar PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), a cikin ƙasa da watanni biyu, an buga takardu sama da 200 akan COVID-19 gami da ilimin ƙwayoyin cuta, ilimin cututtukan cuta, ilimin asali, ganewar asali, da magani tun daga rahoton farko a ranar 7 ga Janairu, 2020 wanda ya ƙayyade jerin ƙwayoyin cuta da aka ware daga marasa lafiya da yawa.
Wannan bita na ƙoƙari ne don taƙaita ci gaban bincike a cikin sabon yanki da ke ci gaba da sauri.
A duk lokacin da zai yiwu, za mu yi ƙoƙarin kwatanta COVID-19 da SARS da wani cuta da CoV ke haifarwa, ciwon numfashi na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS, barkewar cutar a shekarar 2012).
Za mu kuma tattauna abin da muka koya har zuwa yanzu game da rigakafin cutar da kuma yadda za a gane ta da kuma wasu tambayoyi da suka rage da suke da gaggawa.
CoVs an yi la'akari da su a matsayin cututtukan da ba sa kashe mutane, galibi suna haifar da kusan kashi 15% na yawan sanyi 4.
Koyaya, a cikin wannan karni, mun haɗu da CoVs na ɗan adam sau biyu, watau SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, waɗanda suka haifar da barkewar cutar a China a 2003 da Saudi Arabiya a 2012, bi da bi, kuma ba da daɗewa ba suka bazu zuwa wasu ƙasashe da yawa tare da mummunan rashin lafiya da mutuwa.
Saboda haka, cutar COVID-19 ta yanzu ita ce annoba ta uku ta CoV a tarihin mutane.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a Fig. Fig.1,1, an fara bayar da rahoton tarin ciwon huhu wanda ba a san asalinsa ba daga Wuhan a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019 ga Hukumar Lafiya ta Kasa ta China.
Kwana bakwai bayan haka an saki jerin CoV.
A ranar 15 ga Janairu, 2020 ne aka ba da rahoton farkon cutar mutuwa daga Wuhan.
A wannan lokacin, annobar ta bazu cikin sauri zuwa birane, larduna, da kuma ƙasashe da ke kewaye da ita.
A ranar 20 ga watan Janairu, an bayar da rahoton kamuwa da ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya, wanda ke nuna cewa ana iya yaduwa daga mutum zuwa mutum.
A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, an kulle birnin Wuhan tare da dakatar da duk hanyoyin sufuri na jama'a.
A ranar 24 ga Janairu binciken farko na asibiti kan cutar ya ruwaito cewa, daga cikin marasa lafiya 41 da aka tabbatar da cutar, 21 ne kawai suka yi hulɗa kai tsaye da kasuwar abincin teku ta Wuhan wanda aka yi la'akari da wurin fara kamuwa da cutar daga asalin dabba da ba a sani ba.
A ranar 30 ga Janairu, WHO ta ayyana barkewar cutar a matsayin gaggawa ta duniya.
A lokacin da ake rubuta wannan rahoto, cutar ta riga ta bazu a duk fadin kasar Sin da kuma kusan wasu kasashe 50 a duk faɗin duniya (Hoto. (Hoto.2).2).
Tunda halin da ake ciki yana ci gaba da sauri, har yanzu ba a tantance ƙarshen yaduwar cutar da kuma tsananin cutar ba.
A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, binciken cibiyoyi da yawa akan marasa lafiya 8,866 gami da 4,021 da aka tabbatar da marasa lafiya COVID-19 sun gabatar da ƙarin hoto na yau da kullun na annobar kamar haka (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 ya kamu da mutane na kowane zamani, amma galibi a shekarun 30-65.
Kusan rabin (47.7%) na mutanen da suka kamu da cutar sun haura shekaru 50, kaɗan ne kawai ke da shekaru 20 a karkashin, kuma mutane 14 ne kawai suka kamu da cutar da shekarunsu ba su kai 10 ba.
SARS-CoV-2 ya kamu da maza da yawa (0.31/100,000) fiye da mata (0.27/100,000).
COVID-19 ya faɗaɗa a cikin rukuni galibi a cikin Hubei da kewaye.
COVID-19 ya ɗauki matsakaicin kwanaki 5 (2-9) daga farawa zuwa ganewar asali.
Matsakaicin lokacin hawan shine kwanaki 4.8 (3.0-7.2).
Matsakaicin lokaci daga farawa zuwa mutuwa ya kasance kwanaki 9.5 (4.8-13).
Lambar haifuwa ta asali (R0) ta kasance 3.77 (95% CI: 3.51-4.05) kuma daidaitaccen R0 ya kasance 2.23-4.82.
Adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar ya karu sosai kafin 23 ga Janairu, 2020, daidai da lokacin manyan sufuri kafin bikin bazara a China.
Mutuwar marasa lafiya tare da tabbatar da shari'o'i ya kasance 1.44% (95% CI: 1.10-1.86%), kuma daidaitaccen mutuwar dukkan marasa lafiya ya kasance 3.06% (95% CI: 2.02-4.59%).
Manyan abubuwan haɗari guda uku don COVID-19 sune jinsi (maza), shekaru (≥60), da mummunar cutar huhu.
