Bugu da kari, kiyaye daidaiton lantarki, rigakafi da maganin kamuwa da cuta na biyu da kuma girgizar kasa, da kuma kare ayyukan gabobin rayuwa ma na da muhimmanci ga marasa lafiya da SARS-CoV-2.
An san cewa guguwar cytokine sakamakon wuce haddi ne na tsarin garkuwar jiki a cikin marasa lafiya na SARS da MERS.
Cytokine hadari wani nau'i ne na amsawar kumburi ta tsarin da aka nuna ta hanyar sakin jerin cytokines ciki har da TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, da MCP-1.
Wadannan cytokines suna haifar da kwayoyin garkuwar jiki don sakin adadi mai yawa na 'yanci wanda shine babban dalilin ARDS da gazawar gabobin jiki da yawa.
Immunosuppression yana da mahimmanci a cikin maganin guguwar cytokine, musamman a cikin marasa lafiya masu tsanani.
An yi amfani da maganin corticosteroids da tocilizumab, wanda shine anti-IL6 monoclonal antibody, don magance cutar cytokine.
Sauran magungunan hana rigakafi don guguwar cytokine sun haɗa da daidaitawar amsawar rigakafin da aka tsara ta kwayar T; toshewar IFN-γ, IL-1, da TNF; hana JAK; blinatumomab; mai hana siginar cytokine 4; da masu hana HDAC.
