SARS tana da yawan mutuwa fiye da COVID-19 (10.91% vs 1.44%).
Marasa lafiya na COVID-19 suna yada kwayar cutar ko da ba su da alamun cutar yayin da marasa lafiya na SARS ke yin hakan a lokacin da suke da ciwo mai tsanani, wanda ke haifar da matsala mafi girma wajen hana yaduwar COVID-19 fiye da SARS.
Wannan ya bayyana wani ɓangare dalilin da yasa SARS-CoV-2 ya bazu da sauri da yawa fiye da SARS-CoV.
Gwajin RNA na yau da kullun don SARS-CoV-2 na iya zama mara kyau a wasu marasa lafiyar COVID-19.
A gefe guda kuma, marasa lafiya da suka warke na iya sake nuna cewa suna da kwayar cutar.
Wadannan binciken sun kara hadarin yaduwar kwayar cutar sosai.
Ganin irin wannan saurin ci gaba a cikin bincike kan COVID-19, akwai wasu mahimman batutuwa da ke buƙatar warwarewa, kamar haka:
Daga ina SARS-CoV-2 ya fito?
Kodayake an sami kashi 96% na kwayoyin halittar tsakanin SARS-CoV-2 da CoVs biyu masu kama da SARS, har yanzu ba za mu iya yanke shawarar cewa SARS-CoV-2 daga bat ne ba.
Wane dabba ne ya kai cutar daga mahaifar da ta fara, wato, barewa, zuwa ga mutane?
Ba tare da sanin amsoshin 1 da 2 ba, ba za mu iya yanke watsawar yadda ya kamata ba, kuma annobar na iya sakewa a kowane lokaci.
Kodayake samfurin kwayoyin halitta da gwajin kwayoyin sun nuna cewa SARS-CoV-2 yana ɗaure zuwa ACE2, ta yaya ainihin kwayar cutar ta shiga cikin ƙwayoyin hanyar numfashi kuma ta haifar da canje-canje na pathological na gaba?
Shin kwayar cutar tana ɗaure ƙwayoyin ACE2 a wasu gabobin?
Idan ba mu sami amsoshi masu kyau ga waɗannan tambayoyin ba, ba za mu iya samun ganewar asali da kuma magani mai kyau ba.
Har yaushe za a ci gaba da annobar?
Ta yaya kwayar cutar take juyawa a lokacin da take yaduwa tsakanin mutane?
Shin zai zama annoba a duniya, ya mutu kamar SARS ko kuma ya sake dawowa kamar mura?
Yana da muhimmanci amma zai ɗauki lokaci kafin a sami amsoshin waɗannan tambayoyin da kuma wasu da yawa.
Duk da haka, ko da menene kudin da zai iya bukata, ba mu da wani zaɓi sai dai mu dakatar da annobar da wuri-wuri kuma mu dawo da rayuwarmu yadda ta kasance.
Tushen kwayar cutar korona ta mutum
Juyin halittar halitta da daidaitawa sun haifar da juyin halittar kwayar cutar corona (CoVs) da kuma masu masaukinsu, gami da mutane, tsawon dubban shekaru.
Kafin 2003, an san cewa CoVs biyu na mutum (HCoVs) suna haifar da rashin lafiya mai sauƙi, kamar sanyi na yau da kullun.
Barkewar cutar ta mummunar cutar numfashi (SARS) da cutar numfashi ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS) sun juyar da tsabar kudi don bayyana yadda cutar HCoV za ta iya zama mai hallaka da barazana ga rayuwa.
Bayyanar SARS-CoV-2 a tsakiyar China a ƙarshen 2019 ya sake tura CoVs cikin hasken rana kuma ya ba mu mamaki da yawan yaduwar sa amma rage cutar idan aka kwatanta da 'yar'uwar sa SARS-CoV.
Cutar HCoV cuta ce ta dabbobi kuma fahimtar asalin dabbobi na HCoVs zai amfane mu sosai.
Yawancin HCoVs sun samo asali ne daga batutuwan da ba su da cutar.
Hakanan an san matsakaitan masu riƙe da wasu HCoVs.
Gano masu ba da izinin dabbobi yana da tasiri kai tsaye a cikin rigakafin cututtukan mutane.
Binciken hulɗar CoV-host a cikin dabbobi na iya samun muhimmiyar fahimta game da cutar CoV a cikin mutane.
A cikin wannan bita, mun gabatar da bayyani na ilimin da ake da shi game da HCoVs bakwai, tare da mai da hankali kan tarihin gano su da kuma asalin su na dabbobi da kuma watsawa tsakanin jinsuna.
Abu mai mahimmanci, muna kwatanta da kuma bambance-bambancen HCoVs daban-daban daga hangen nesa na juyin halitta na kwayar cuta da kuma sake haɗuwa da kwayoyin halitta.
An tattauna game da annobar cutar CoV ta 2019 (COVID-19) a wannan mahallin.
Bugu da kari, an kuma nuna bukatun sauya mai masaukin da ya yi nasara da kuma tasirin juyin halittar kwayar cutar kan tsananin cutar.
Coronaviruses (CoVs) na cikin dangin Coronaviridae, wanda ya ƙunshi rukuni na ɓoye, mai kyau-sensing, ƙwayoyin cuta na RNA guda ɗaya.
Wadannan ƙwayoyin cuta masu babban kwayar halitta na kilobases 26 zuwa 32 a tsakanin ƙwayoyin cuta na RNA an kira su CoVs saboda yanayin halittarsu kamar kambi a ƙarƙashin microscope na lantarki.
A tsarin, CoVs suna da kwayoyin halittar da ba su da rarrabuwa waɗanda ke da irin wannan ƙungiyar.
Kimanin kashi biyu bisa uku na kwayoyin sun ƙunshi manyan manyan sararin karatu biyu (ORF1a da ORF1b), waɗanda aka fassara zuwa pp1a da pp1ab polyproteins.
Ana ƙara sarrafa polyproteins don samar da sunadarai 16 marasa tsari, waɗanda aka sanya nsp1 ~ 16.
Sauran ɓangaren kwayoyin sun ƙunshi ORFs don sunadarai na tsari, ciki har da ƙugiya (S), envelope (E), membrane (M) da nucleoprotein (N).
Hakanan wasu ƙwayoyin cuta na musamman na ƙwayoyin cuta suna yin lambar ta hanyar nau'ikan CoV daban-daban.
Dangane da bambancin jerin sunadarai, ana rarraba CoVs zuwa nau'i huɗu (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV da delta-CoV), daga cikinsu nau'in beta-CoV ya ƙunshi yawancin HCoVs kuma an rarraba shi zuwa jinsi huɗu (A, B, C da D).
Shaidar ilimin halittu ta nuna cewa batsa da masu naman gwari sune tushen kwayoyin halittar mafi yawan alpha-CoVs da beta-CoVs, yayin da tsuntsaye su ne babban wurin ajiyar gamma-CoVs da delta-CoVs.
Shekaru dubbai, CoVs koyaushe suna ƙetare shingen nau'in kuma wasu sun fito a matsayin mahimman ƙwayoyin cuta na ɗan adam.
Zuwa yau, an san mutane bakwai na CoVs (HCoVs).
Daga cikinsu HCoV-229E da HCoV-NL63 sune alpha-CoVs.
Sauran beta-CoVs guda biyar sun hada da HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, coronavirus mai tsanani na cututtukan numfashi (SARS-CoV), coronavirus na cututtukan numfashi na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS-CoV) da SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 da HCoV-NL63 yawanci suna haifar da alamun rashin lafiya, kamar sanyi da / ko zawo.
Akasin haka, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV da sabon SARS-CoV-2 da aka gano suna da cututtuka sosai, suna haifar da kamuwa da cuta mai tsanani a ƙananan hanyoyin numfashi a cikin marasa lafiya da yawa tare da babban damar samun ciwon ciwon numfashi mai tsanani (ARDS) da bayyanar extrapulmonary.
An ware kwayar HCoV-229E ta farko, B814, daga fitowar hanci na marasa lafiya da sanyi a tsakiyar shekarun 1960.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, an tara ƙarin ilimi ta hanyar bincike mai zurfi akan HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43, dukansu suna haifar da alamun da ke iyakance kansu.
Tabbas, an yarda da ra'ayin cewa kamuwa da HCoVs gabaɗaya ba shi da lahani har zuwa barkewar SARS.
Barkewar SARS da ta faru a 2003 na ɗaya daga cikin mafi muni a tarihin yanzu, ta kamu da mutane sama da 8,000 tare da mutuwar kusan kashi 10%.
Shekaru goma bayan haka, annobar cutar numfashi ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS) ta haifar da wata annoba mai ci gaba a yankin Larabawa tare da yaduwa zuwa sauran duniya.
Sabuwar cutar HCoV (2019-nCoV) ta 2019, wacce daga baya aka sake masa suna SARS-CoV-2, ita ce mai haifar da annobar cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wacce ta kashe mutane sama da 3,120 kuma ta kamu da mutane sama da 91,000 har zuwa ranar 3 ga Maris, 2020.
An yi gargadin kuma duniya dole ta shirya don annobar SARS-CoV-2 mai zuwa.
Dukkanin kwayar cutar HCoVs bakwai suna da asalin zoonotic daga bat, beraye ko dabbobin gida.
Layin shaidu da yawa suna tallafawa asalin juyin halitta na duk HCoVs daga bat, inda ƙwayoyin cuta suka dace da kyau kuma ba su da cutar amma suna nuna bambancin kwayoyin halitta.
Cutar COVID-19 ta gabatar da kalubale masu yawa na likita, kimiyya, zamantakewa da ɗabi'a ga Sin da duniya.
Binciken asalin kwayar cutar HCoVs na samar da tsari don fahimtar tarihin halitta, motsa jiki da abubuwan da ke hana nau'in tsalle.
Wannan kuma na iya jagorantar ko sauƙaƙa bincike don mai riƙewa, matsakaici da haɓaka mai masaukin dabba na SARS-CoV-2, tare da mahimman abubuwan da ke tattare da hana ɓarkewar nan gaba.
A cikin wannan bita mun gabatar da bayyani game da asalin zoonotic, watsawa tsakanin jinsuna da kuma cutar HCoVs.
Musamman, muna nunawa da tattauna batun gama gari cewa ƙwayoyin cuta na HCoVs yawanci ba su da cutar a cikin masu masaukin su na halitta amma sun zama masu cutar bayan watsawa tsakanin nau'ikan zuwa sabon mai masauki.
Hakanan muna nazarin yanayin juyin HCoV wanda yawanci ƙaruwar yaduwar cuta ke zuwa tare da raguwar cutar.
An kuma tattauna sakamakon barkewar cutar SARS-CoV-2 a wannan mahallin.
An san CoVs na dabbobi tun daga ƙarshen 1930s.
Kafin warewar farko na HCoV-229E nau'in B814 daga fitar hanci na marasa lafiya waɗanda suka kamu da mura, an ware CoVs daban-daban a cikin dabbobi daban-daban da suka kamu da cutar, gami da turkey, linzamin kwamfuta, shanu, alade, cat da kare.
A cikin shekarun da suka gabata, an gano HCoVs bakwai.
