An ware kwayar HCoV-229E ta farko daga hanyoyin numfashi na marasa lafiya tare da kamuwa da cutar ta sama a cikin shekarar 1966, kuma daga baya aka daidaita shi don girma a cikin layukan ƙwayoyin huhu na WI-38.
Marasa lafiya da ke dauke da HCoV-229E sun nuna alamun sanyi na yau da kullun, gami da ciwon kai, tari, rashin jin daɗi da ciwon wuya, tare da zazzabi da tari da aka gani a cikin 10 ~ 20% na lokuta.
Daga baya a cikin 1967, an ware HCoV-OC43 daga al'adun gabobin jiki da kuma hanyar wucewa ta gaba a cikin kwakwalwar berayen da ke shayarwa.
Abubuwan asibiti na kamuwa da cutar HCoV-OC43 sun yi kama da waɗanda HCoV-229E ya haifar, waɗanda ba za a iya bambanta su da kamuwa da wasu cututtukan cututtukan numfashi kamar su ƙwayoyin cuta na mura A da rhinoviruses.
Dukansu HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43 an rarraba su a duniya, kuma galibi ana watsa su a lokacin hunturu a yanayin zafi.
Gabaɗaya, lokacin haɓakawa na waɗannan ƙwayoyin cuta guda biyu bai kai mako ɗaya ba, sannan kusan sati 2 na rashin lafiya.
Dangane da binciken da aka yi akan masu sa kai, mutane masu lafiya da suka kamu da HCoV-229E sun sami sanyi mai sauƙi.
Wasu marasa lafiya kaɗan ne kawai da ke da rauni na rigakafi suka nuna mummunan kamuwa da cutar ta ƙananan hanyoyin numfashi.
SARS, wanda kuma aka sani da atypical pneumonia, shine farkon cutar da HCoV ta haifar a tarihin ɗan adam kuma mai haifar da cutar shine SARS-CoV, HCoV na uku da aka gano.
Ana iya gano farkon yanayin SARS a ƙarshen 2002 a lardin Guangdong na China.
Cutar SARS ta haifar da mutane 8,096 da aka ruwaito tare da mutuwar mutane 774, wanda ya bazu a ƙasashe da nahiyoyi da yawa.
Baya ga masu yaduwa, an kiyasta cewa kowane hali na iya haifar da kusan lokuta biyu na biyu, tare da lokacin ɗagawa na kwanaki 4 zuwa 7 kuma mafi girman nauyin kwayar cutar yana bayyana a ranar 10 na cutar.
Marasa lafiya da ke dauke da cutar SARS-CoV da farko suna da ciwon zuciya, ciwon kai, zazzabi, rashin jin daɗi da kuma sanyi, sannan kuma suna da dyspnea, tari da wahalar numfashi a matsayin alamun rashin lafiya.
Lymphopenia, gwajin aikin hanta da aka lalata, da kuma ƙaruwa na creatine kinase sune cututtukan da aka saba samu a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje na SARS.
An kuma lura da lalacewar alveolar mai yaduwa, yaduwar ƙwayoyin epithelial da ƙaruwa na macrophages a cikin marasa lafiya na SARS.
Kimanin kashi 20-30% na marasa lafiya daga baya suna buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani da iska mai iska.
Baya ga ƙananan hanyoyin numfashi, gabobin da yawa ciki har da na hanji, hanta da koda suma za a iya kamuwa da su a cikin waɗannan maganganun masu tsanani, yawanci tare da guguwar cytokine, wanda zai iya zama mai kisa musamman a cikin marasa lafiya marasa ƙarfi.
An fara ware kwayar cutar daga kwayar cutar huhu ta dangi na mai cutar wanda ya yi tafiya zuwa Hong Kong daga Guangzhou.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, an yi ƙoƙari sosai don binciken HCoV.
An ware HCoV-NL63 daga wani yaro mai wata 7 daga Netherlands a ƙarshen 2004.
Da farko an gano cewa ya fi yawa a cikin yara ƙanana, tsofaffi da marasa lafiya masu rashin ƙarfi tare da cututtukan numfashi.
