Wani bincike mai zaman kansa ya bayyana ware wannan kwayar cutar daga samfurin hanci daga wani yaro mai wata 8 da ke fama da ciwon huhu a Netherlands.
Ko da yake an gano shi a Netherlands, an rarraba shi a duniya.
An kiyasta cewa HCoV-NL63 yana da kusan kashi 4.7% na cututtukan numfashi na yau da kullun, kuma mafi girman abin da ya faru yana faruwa a farkon bazara, bazara da hunturu.
HCoV-NL63 yana da alaƙa da cutar laryngitis mai hanawa, wanda kuma aka sani da croup.
