Gabaɗaya, lokacin da waɗannan HCoVs suka sami damar watsawa yadda ya kamata kuma su ci gaba da kasancewa cikin mutane, suma suna zama marasa cutarwa ko masu cutarwa.
An fara ware MERS-CoV a shekarar 2012 daga huhu na wani mai shekaru 60 wanda ya kamu da cutar huhu mai tsanani da kuma rashin aikin koda a Saudi Arabia.
Yayinda yawancin magungunan da aka tabbatar da su daga dakin gwaje-gwaje suka fito ne daga Gabas ta Tsakiya, an ba da rahoton shigo da magungunan da ke da wasu lokuta na biyu zuwa kusanci da kusanci a ƙasashen Turai da Tunisia.
Wani fashewar na biyu ya faru a Koriya ta Kudu a 2015 tare da tabbatar da lamuran 186.
Bayyanar asibiti na MERS suna kama da na SARS, wanda ke nuna ci gaba da ciwon huhu mai tsanani.
Ba kamar SARS ba, marasa lafiya da yawa da ke da MERS suma sun sami gagarumar rashin aikin koda, wanda ya zuwa yanzu ya zama na musamman ga MERS tsakanin cututtukan da HCoV ke haifarwa.
Fiye da kashi 30% na marasa lafiya suna da alamun gastrointestinal, kamar zawo da zubar da ciki.
Ya zuwa 14 ga Fabrairu, 2020, sama da mutane 2500 da aka tabbatar da su a dakin gwaje-gwaje an bayar da rahoton su tare da yawan mutuwar mutum 34.4%, wanda ya sanya MERS-CoV daya daga cikin cututtukan da suka fi muni da aka sani ga mutane.
A tsakiyar zuwa ƙarshen Disamba 2019, an gano gungun marasa lafiya masu ciwon huhu da aka sani a baya cewa suna da alaƙa da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 a Wuhan, Lardin Hubei, China.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ayyana barkewar cutar kamuwa da cutar ta ƙananan hanyoyin numfashi da SARS-CoV-2 ya haifar da gaggawa ta lafiyar jama'a na damuwa ta duniya kuma ta kuma sanya sunan cutar COVID-19.
Ya zuwa ranar 3 ga Maris, 2020, an tabbatar da kamuwa da cutar 90,053 a duk duniya, tare da mutuwar mutum 3.4%.
Musamman ma, mutuwar cutar a Hubei, China ta kai kashi 4.2%, yayin da wacce ke wajen ta ta kai kashi 1.2%.
SARS-CoV-2 na haifar da mummunar kamuwa da cuta ta numfashi kamar SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, wanda aka gabatar a matsayin zazzabi, tari da dyspnea.
Hakanan ana ganin zawo a wasu marasa lafiya.
Ciwon huhu yana ɗaya daga cikin mafi munin alamun kuma yana iya ci gaba cikin sauri zuwa ciwon rashin ƙarfi na numfashi.
Kodayake SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2 suna da kamanceceniya sosai saboda babban daidaiton jerin nucleotide na 82%, sun haɗu cikin rassa daban-daban a cikin itacen phylogenetic.
SARS-CoV-2 a bayyane yake ba shi da cutar amma yana da saurin yaduwa idan aka kwatanta da SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV.
An bayar da rahoton mutanen da ba su da alamun cutar SARS-CoV-2 kuma suna iya taimakawa wajen saurin yaduwar cutar a duniya.
Kwatanta SARS-CoV-2 da sauran HCoVs shida da kuma bambance-bambance sun bayyana kamance da bambance-bambance masu ban sha'awa sosai.
Na farko, lokacin ɗorawa da tsawon lokacin cutar HCoV suna kama da juna.
Dangane da wannan, SARS-CoV-2 yana bin babban yanayin sauran HCoVs shida.
Na biyu, tsananin bayyanar cututtukan COVID-19 ya ta'allaka ne tsakanin SARS-CoV da HCoVs huɗu da aka samu a cikin al'umma (watau HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 da HCoV-NL63).
A gefe guda, kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2 yana nuna halaye waɗanda galibi ana gani yayin kamuwa da cutar HCoVs da aka samu a cikin al'umma, gami da gabatar da rashin takamaiman, mai sauƙi ko ma babu alamun.
A gefe guda, ana iya ganin ƙaramin ƙaramin ƙananan maganganun COVID-19 masu tsanani kamar yadda yake a cikin cutar SARS-CoV, kodayake rabo ya ɗan ƙasa.
Na uku, watsa SARS-CoV-2 kuma yana nuna halaye masu ban sha'awa na halaye na HCoVs da SARS-CoV da aka samu a cikin al'umma.
A gefe guda, yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 aƙalla tana da girma kamar na HCoVs da aka samu a cikin al'umma.
A gefe guda, har yanzu ana tabbatar da ko yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 ta ragu bayan wucewa a cikin mutane kamar yadda yake a cikin shari'o'in SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV.
A ƙarshe, kamar sauran HCoVs, ana iya gano SARS-CoV-2 a cikin samfuran ƙwayoyin cuta.
Ko watsa SARS-CoV-2 ta hanyar kwance yana taka muhimmiyar rawa kamar yadda yake a cikin yanayin SARS-CoV aƙalla a wasu yanayi har yanzu ana bayyana shi ta hanyar nazarin gaba.
Hakanan yana da matukar sha'awa don ganin ko SARS-CoV-2 na iya nuna yanayi kamar yadda yake a cikin yanayin HCoVs da aka samu a cikin al'umma.
Duk da haka, fasalulluka na SARS-CoV-2 gami da yaduwar sa, cutar da ke haifar da cutar da kuma ci gaba da yaduwa bayan wucewa a cikin mutane zai yi tasiri a kan makomar barkewar cutar COVID-19.
Dukkanin HCoVs huɗu da aka samu a cikin al'umma waɗanda ke haifar da ƙananan alamun sun dace da mutane.
Daga wani hangen nesa, yana iya zama gaskiya cewa mutane sun dace da waɗannan HCoVs huɗu.
A wasu kalmomi, duka biyun na iya zama waɗanda suka tsira daga tsoffin annobar HCoV.
An kawar da HCoVs da ke haifar da cututtuka masu tsanani a cikin mutane da kuma mutane waɗanda suka sami cututtukan HCoV masu tsanani.
Don wannan ya faru, HCoVs dole ne su ninka a cikin mutane har zuwa isa don ba da damar tarawa na juyin halittar da ke daidaitawa wanda ke magance abubuwan ƙuntatawa na mai masaukin baki.
A wannan ma'anar, tsawon lokacin da annobar SARS-CoV-2 ke ci gaba da yaduwa kuma mutane da yawa da ta kamu da su, mafi girman damar da za ta daidaita da mutane.
