Bambancin waɗannan sunadarai masu karɓar bakuncin tsakanin mutane da masu karɓar bakuncin HCoVs na halitta kamar su bat, raƙuman ruwa da masu tsutsa na iya zama shinge ga watsawa tsakanin jinsuna.
HCoVs dole ne su mamaye abubuwan dogaro da mai masaukin baki da kuma lalata abubuwan da ke hana mai masaukin baki don samun nasarar watsawa tsakanin jinsuna.
A wannan batun, abubuwan da ke saurin bayyana kwayoyin a wannan muhimmin yanki na hulɗar kwayar cutar-mai masaukin baki har yanzu suna buƙatar ganowa da kuma bayyana su.
Binciken da ba shi da son zuciya na tushen mai masaukin baki da abubuwan ƙuntatawa don SARS-CoV-2 ta amfani da fasahar zamani ta CRISPR na iya zama mai amfani.
Fitowar sabbin HCoVs: koma zuwa ƙasa
Bambancin bat CoVs yana ba da dama mai yawa don fitowar sabbin HCoVs.
A wannan ma'anar, bat CoVs suna aiki a matsayin tarin kwayoyin HCoVs.
Bugu da kari, saurin canji da kuma sake hada kwayoyin halitta suma suna motsa ci gaban HCoV kuma suna aiki a matsayin matakai biyu masu mahimmanci a cikin wannan tsari.
Misali, saye ko rasa sabbin kwayoyin da ke yin kwayar halitta na da damar sauya fasalin kwayar cutar sosai.
Daga cikin sunadarai masu amfani da SARS-CoV, ORF8 an yi tunanin yana da mahimmanci wajen daidaitawa ga mutane, kamar yadda aka ware ƙwayoyin cutar bat da ke da alaƙa da SARS-CoV amma an gano cewa suna ɓoye sunadarai ORF8 masu banbanci.
An sami fasalin cire kwayar cutar 29-nucleotide na SARS-CoVs a cikin nau'ikan da aka ware a farkon annobar ɗan adam.
Wannan sharewa ya raba ORF8 zuwa ORF8a da ORF8b kuma ana tsammanin ya zama maye gurbin da ke inganta sauyawar mai masaukin baki.
Bayan haka, SARS-CoV yana da tarihin sake haɗuwa tare da layin alpha- da gamma-CoVs, inda aka gano adadi mai yawa na ƙananan yankuna masu haɗuwa a cikin RNA mai dogara da RNA polymerase.
An kuma gano wuraren sake haɗawa a cikin nsp9, yawancin nsp10, da sassan nsp14.
