Baya ga SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, an kuma lura da abubuwan sake haɗuwa a cikin wasu HCoVs, wanda HCoVs ke sake haɗuwa da sauran CoVs na dabbobi a cikin ƙwayoyin halittar su.
Ya kamata kuma a yi gargadin cewa zabin wucin gadi na iya taimakawa ga canje-canje da ba a so ba a cikin kwayoyin halittar kwayar cutar, wanda wataƙila sakamakon sauƙaƙe ƙwayoyin cuta daga matsin zaɓin da aka yi, kamar ta tsarin garkuwar jiki.
Misali na waɗannan tasirin shine asarar ORF4 mai cikakken tsayi a cikin kwayar kwayar HCoV-229E, saboda cire nucleotide biyu.
Duk da yake ana iya lura da ORF4 mara lalacewa a cikin ƙwayoyin cuta na bat da raƙumi da ke da alaƙa da HCoV-229E, alpha-CoV na alpaca yana nuna shigar da nucleotide guda ɗaya, wanda ke haifar da sauya fasalin.
