Hakanan za a iya samun ƙarin nau'ikan CoV masu cutarwa ta hanyar sake haɗuwa, wanda ke haifar da samun sabbin sunadarai ko fasalin sunadarai don daidaitawar mai masaukin baki.
Saboda haka, ba daidaituwa ba ce cewa sabbin HCoVs guda uku sun bayyana a cikin shekaru ashirin da suka gabata.
CoVs ba su da cutar ko kuma suna haifar da wasu alamun rashin lafiya a cikin masu masaukin su kamar su bat da rakuma.
Suna yin kwafi sosai ba tare da haifar da amsawar garkuwar jiki mai ƙarfi ba.
A nan ne asirin dalilin da ya sa ake ganin masu dauke da cutar ba tare da bayyanar cututtuka ba da kuma abin da ke haifar da munanan cututtuka a cikin mutane.
Alamun cutar sun fi yawa saboda yawan amsawar garkuwar jiki da kuma guguwar cytokine inda mafi ƙarfin amsawar garkuwar jiki, mafi munin lalacewar huhu.
Akasin haka, a cikin masu ɗaukar asymptomatic, an cire martani na rigakafi daga kwafin CoV.
Irin wannan dabarar cire haɗin amsawar rigakafi na iya samun fa'ida a maganin anti-SARS-CoV-2.
