Fitowar SARS-CoV-2 ya bi babban jigon da SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV suka tashi.
Yayin da aka sami bat beta-CoV wanda ke da kashi 95% na nucleotide homology tare da SARS-CoV, akwai kuma bat-CoV wanda ke da kashi 96% na nucleotide homology tare da SARS-CoV-2.
Duk da yake an gano cewa civets da sauran dabbobi a kasuwa suna da ƙwayoyin cuta iri ɗaya da SARS-CoV, ba a gano masu watsa shiri na tsakiya na SARS-CoV-2 ba.
An gano beta-CoVs na pangolin da ke da kama da SARS-CoV-2, wanda ke nuna cewa pangolins na iya zama ɗaya daga cikin masu masaukin baki ko kuma beta-CoVs na pangolin na iya ba da gudummawar ɓangarorin kwayoyin zuwa sigar ƙarshe ta SARS-CoV-2.
Kodayake tambayoyi sun kasance, babu wata hujja da ke nuna cewa SARS-CoV-2 mutum ne ya yi shi ko da gangan ko kuma ba da gangan ba.
CoVs sun dawo cikin hasken rana saboda barkewar cutar SARS-CoV-2 kwanan nan.
Nazarin CoVs a cikin bat da sauran dabbobi ya canza ra'ayinmu sosai game da mahimmancin asalin zoonotic da wuraren ajiyar dabbobi na HCoVs a cikin watsawar ɗan adam.
Shaida mai yawa ta nuna cewa SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2 suna da asalin bat kuma ana watsa su ga mutane ta hanyar masu watsawa na tsakiya.
Ganin cewa kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV ta samo asali ne daga hulɗa tsakanin mutane da civets a cikin kasuwanni, rufe kasuwannin da ke da ruwa da kashe civets a ciki na iya kawo ƙarshen annobar SARS.
Ta hanyar irin wannan tunani, ya kamata a cire pangolins daga kasuwannin da ke da ruwa don hana yaduwar cutar zoonotic, saboda gano zuriya da yawa na beta-CoVs na pangolin da ke da alaƙa da SARS-CoV-2.
Koyaya, ko kuma yadda SARS-CoV-2 ke yaduwa ga mutane ta hanyar pangolins da sauran dabbobi masu shayarwa har yanzu ana bayyana su a cikin bincike na gaba.
A gefe guda, MERS-CoV ya wanzu a cikin raƙuman dromedary na dogon lokaci.
Waɗannan raƙuma suna da muhimmanci wajen sufuri da kuma tushen nama, madara, fata da kuma kayan ɗamara ga mazauna yankin.
An rarraba su sosai a duk Gabas ta Tsakiya da Afirka.
Saboda haka ba zai yiwu a yi hadaya da dukkan rakuma ba don sarrafa MERS, kamar yadda aka yi a kasuwannin dabbobin daji a China don hana yaduwar SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2.
Don dakatar da sake fashewar cutar ta MERS, ya kamata a bi cikakkiyar hanya don samar da ingantattun alluran rigakafi kan MERS-CoV don raƙuma, tare da sauran matakan sarrafa kamuwa da cuta.
Tun da ba za mu iya kawar da wadannan ƙwayoyin cuta ba, za a iya samun sababbin nau'o'in kwayoyin halittar da za su iya haifar da barkewar cutar.
An samu nau'ikan nau'ikan CoVs masu cutar dabbobi a cikin daji.
Musamman, bat CoVs tare da yiwuwar zoonotic suna da bambanci sosai.
Akwai dama da yawa da waɗannan CoVs na zoonotic ke haɓaka da sake haɗuwa, wanda ke haifar da fitowar sabbin CoVs waɗanda ke da saurin watsawa da / ko masu kisa a cikin mutane a nan gaba.
Ya kamata a daina cin dabbobi a wasu wurare na kasar Sin domin rage hulda da dabbobi ba dole ba.
Tare da wahalar SARS, MERS da COVID-19, ya kamata a samar da kyakkyawan shiri da shirin amsawa.
A gaskiya ma, ƙwayoyin cuta da yawa sun wanzu a duniya na dogon lokaci.
Suna zama a cikin ɗakunan ajiyarsu na halitta har sai akwai damar watsawa.
Ko da yake wutsiyoyi suna da abubuwa da yawa da suke sa mutane su yaɗa ƙwayoyin cuta, za a iya rage haɗuwa da wutsiyoyi da sauran dabbobi idan aka koya wa mutane su guje musu.
Ana buƙatar ci gaba da sa ido a cikin dabbobi masu shayarwa don fahimtar yanayin halittu na CoVs da kuma masu masaukin su na halitta, wanda zai zama da amfani wajen hana yaduwar dabbobi zuwa mutane da kuma barkewar cutar nan gaba.
A ƙarshe, hanya mafi inganci don hana cutar zoonosis ta kwayar cuta ita ce mutane su nisanta kansu daga wuraren da ke da alaƙa da yanayin halittu na ƙwayoyin cuta masu cutar.
Har yanzu akwai wasu abubuwa da suka ɓace a cikin jigon asalin cutar SARS-CoV-2.
Da farko, idan dabbobin daji sun watsa kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 ga pangolins, zai zama mai ban sha'awa a ga a wane yanayi dabbobin daji da pangolins zasu iya raba wuri guda na muhalli.
Na biyu, idan dabbobin da ke wasa suna taka rawa a kai tsaye wajen yaduwar cutar ga mutane, ya kamata a tantance yadda mutane ke hulɗa da su.
Na uku, idan dabba mai shayarwa ta uku tana aiki a matsayin mai masaukin baki na gaske, yadda take hulɗa da nau'ikan daban-daban ciki har da mutane, bat da pangolins dole ne a bayyana.
A ƙarshe, tun da yawancin dabbobi masu shayarwa ciki har da dabbobin gida na iya zama masu saukin kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2, ya kamata a gudanar da sa ido da kuma kamuwa da gwaji.
Idan ya kasance bat, pangolin ko wani dabba mai shayarwa, ana sa ran cewa SARS-CoV-2 ko kuma kwayoyin cutarsa na iyaye waɗanda suke kusan iri ɗaya za a gano su a cikin masu masaukin halitta a nan gaba.
Ci gaba da bincike a wannan fannin zai bayyana hanyar juyin halitta na SARS-CoV-2 a cikin dabbobi, tare da muhimman tasiri a cikin rigakafi da sarrafa COVID-19 a cikin mutane.
Ana buƙatar sabunta ka'idodin ganewar asali na COVID-19 kasar da ake zargi da kasar da aka tabbatar
A ranar 6 ga Fabrairu, 2020, ƙungiyarmu ta buga jagorar shawarwari mai sauri don ganewar asali da magani na kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (2019-nCoV) na 2019, kuma wannan jagorar ta ba da kwarewarmu kuma ta zama kyakkyawan tunani don yaƙi da wannan annobar a duk duniya.
Koyaya, cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19) sabuwar cuta ce, wayewarmu da iliminmu suna ƙaruwa a hankali bisa ga binciken bincike da ke gudana da kwarewar asibiti; saboda haka, dabarun ganewar asali da magani suma ana ci gaba da sabunta su.
A cikin wannan wasika, mun amsa wata sanarwa game da jagorarmu kuma mun samar da sabbin ka'idojin gano cutar na kasar da ake zargi da kasar da aka tabbatar da ita bisa ga sabon Ka'idojin Gano cutar da kuma Kula da COVID-19 (na bakwai) wanda Kwamitin Lafiya na Jamhuriyar Jama'ar Sin ya fitar.
A watan Disamba na shekarar 2019, sabon coronavirus (2019-nCoV) ya haifar da barkewar cutar, wanda yanzu aka sanya masa suna a hukumance da cutar coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) kuma an sanya wa kwayar cutar sunan coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
