A ranar Alhamis, jimillar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 coronavirus ya zarce miliyan daya a duniya, kamar yadda bayanan Jami'ar Johns Hopkins suka nuna.
Akalla mutane dubu 52 ne suka mutu sakamakon cutar COVID-19, cutar da coronavirus ta haifar.
Wannan muhimmin abu ya zo ne a ranar da Malawi ta tabbatar da kamuwa da cutar coronavirus ta farko kuma Zambia ta samu mutuwar ta farko da ke da nasaba da cutar coronavirus.
