" Kodayake kalmar " annobar" kawai tana nufin yadda cutar ta yadu, ba yadda hatsarin wasu lokuta yake ba, WHO ta lura da bukatar tura gwamnatoci zuwa aiki: "
" "Dukkanin kasashe na iya canza yanayin wannan annobar. "
