Cutar cutar coronavirus ta 2019-20 annoba ce mai gudana ta cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wacce cutar coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) mai tsanani ta haifar.
An gano barkewar cutar a Wuhan, China, a watan Disamba na 2019, an ayyana ta a matsayin Matsalar Lafiya ta Duniya ta Damuwa ta Duniya a ranar 30 ga Janairu, 2020, kuma an gane ta a matsayin annoba a ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020.
Ya zuwa 10 ga Afrilu 2020, an bayar da rahoton kimanin mutane miliyan 1.61 da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a kasashe da yankuna 210, wanda ya haifar da mutuwar mutane kusan 97,000.
Kimanin mutane 364,000 ne suka warke.
An kiyasta yawan mutuwar cutar ya kai kashi 4 cikin 100 a China, yayin da a duniya ya kasance daga 13.04% a Aljeriya zuwa .08% a New Zealand.
