Abubuwan rikitarwa na iya haɗawa da ciwon huhu da kuma ciwon numfashi mai tsanani.
Lokaci daga bayyanar cutar zuwa bayyanar cututtuka yawanci kusan kwanaki biyar ne, amma na iya kasancewa daga kwana biyu zuwa goma sha huɗu.
Babu maganin rigakafi ko takamaiman maganin rigakafin cutar.
Maganin farko shine maganin cututtuka da tallafi. Matakan rigakafi da aka ba da shawarar sun hada da wanke hannu, rufe bakin mutum lokacin da yake tari, kiyaye nesa da sauran mutane, da kuma sa ido da keɓe kai ga mutanen da suke zargin cewa suna da kamuwa da cutar.
Hukumomi a dukan duniya sun amsa ta wajen kafa takunkumin tafiye-tafiye, keɓewa, dokar hana fita, sarrafa haɗarin aiki, da kuma rufe wuraren aiki.
Cutar ta haifar da mummunar rushewar tattalin arziki da zamantakewar duniya, jinkirta ko soke abubuwan wasanni, addini, siyasa da al'adu, da kuma karancin kayayyaki da aka fadada ta hanyar sayen firgici.
Makarantu da jami'o'i sun rufe ko dai a ƙasa ko a gida a ƙasashe 193, wanda ya shafi kusan kashi 99.4 na ɗaliban duniya.
Rashin fahimta game da kwayar cutar ya bazu a yanar gizo, kuma an sami abubuwan da suka shafi kyamar baki da nuna wariya ga Sinawa, wasu mutane na Gabas da Kudu maso Gabashin Asiya da kuma bayyanar, da sauransu daga yankunan da ke da manyan shari'o'in kwayar cutar.
Saboda rage tafiye tafiye da rufe masana'antu masu nauyi, an sami raguwar gurbataccen iska da fitowar carbon.
Hukumomin kiwon lafiya a Wuhan, China (babban birnin lardin Hubei) sun ba da rahoton tarin cututtukan ciwon huhu na sanadin da ba a sani ba a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, kuma an fara bincike a farkon Janairu, 2020.
Yawancin shari'o'in suna da alaƙa da Kasuwar Siyar da Kayan Kifin Huanan kuma saboda haka ana tsammanin kwayar cutar tana da asalin zoonotic.
Kwayar cutar da ta haifar da barkewar cutar ana kiranta SARS-CoV-2, sabuwar cutar da aka gano wacce ke da alaƙa da kwayar cutar bat coronaviruses, pangolin coronaviruses, da SARS-CoV. An gano daga baya cewa farkon mutumin da ke da alamun cutar ya kamu da cutar a ranar 1 ga Disamba, 2019, kuma wannan mutumin ba shi da alaƙa da alamar kasuwar da ta biyo baya.
Daga farkon rukunin shari'o'in da aka ruwaito a watan Disamba na 2019, kashi biyu bisa uku an gano cewa suna da alaƙa da kasuwa.
A ranar 13 ga Maris, 2020, wani rahoto da ba a tabbatar da shi ba daga South China Morning Post ya nuna cewa wani shari'ar da aka gano a ranar 17 ga Nuwamba, 2019, a cikin wani mutum mai shekaru 55 daga lardin Hubei, na iya zama na farko. A ranar 26 ga Fabrairu, 2020, WHO ta ba da rahoton cewa, yayin da aka ba da rahoton cewa sabbin shari'o'in sun ragu a China amma ba zato ba tsammani sun karu a Italiya, Iran, da Koriya ta Kudu, adadin sabbin shari'o'in da ke wajen China ya wuce adadin sabbin shari'o'in a cikin China a karon farko.
Za a iya samun karancin rahoto na cututtuka, musamman a tsakanin waɗanda ke da alamun rashin lafiya.
A ranar 26 ga watan Fabrairu, an samu rahotanni na ƙarancin cututtuka a tsakanin matasa, waɗanda shekarunsu 19 da ƙasa da haka sun kai kashi 2.4% na cututtuka a duniya. Babban mai ba da shawara kan kimiyya na Burtaniya, Patrick Vallance, ya kiyasta cewa kashi 60% na yawan mutanen Burtaniya za su buƙaci kamuwa da cutar kafin a sami tasirin garken garken.
Al'amuran suna nufin adadin mutanen da aka gwada wa COVID-19, kuma wanda aka tabbatar da gwajin sa yana da inganci bisa ga ka'idojin hukuma.
Ya zuwa ranar 23 ga watan Maris, babu wata ƙasa da ta gwada fiye da kashi 3% na yawan jama'arta, kuma ƙasashe da yawa suna da manufofin hukuma na rashin gwada waɗanda ke da ƙananan alamun cutar, kamar Italiya, Netherlands, Spain, da Switzerland.
Wani bincike da aka buga a ranar 16 ga watan Maris ya gano cewa a kasar Sin, har zuwa ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, kimanin kashi 86% na kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 ba a gano su ba, kuma wadannan kamuwa da cuta da ba a rubuta su ba ne tushen kamuwa da cutar a kashi 79% na wadanda aka rubuta su.
Wani bincike na kididdiga da aka buga a ranar 30 ga Maris ya kiyasta cewa adadin kamuwa da cutar a Italiya ya fi adadin da aka ruwaito.
Kwanan nan an kiyasta cewa yawan haifuwa (R0) na COVID-19 ya kai 1.4 zuwa 2.4.
Wani bincike da Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Amurka ta wallafa ya kammala cewa zai iya zama 5.7.
Yawancin mutane da ke da COVID-19 suna murmurewa.
Ga waɗanda ba su yi ba, lokacin daga bayyanar cututtuka zuwa mutuwa ya kasance tsakanin kwanaki 6 zuwa 41, tare da mafi yawan kwanaki 14 .
Ya zuwa 10 ga Afrilu 2020, kusan mutane 97,000 ne suka mutu sakamakon COVID-19.
A China, har zuwa 5 ga Fabrairu, kusan kashi 80% na mutuwar sun kasance a cikin waɗanda suka haura shekaru 60, kuma kashi 75% suna da yanayin kiwon lafiya da suka riga sun kasance ciki har da cututtukan zuciya da ciwon sukari. Ƙididdigar hukuma na mutuwar daga cutar COVID-19 gabaɗaya tana nufin mutanen da suka mutu waɗanda suka gwada tabbatacce ga COVID bisa ga ka'idojin hukuma.
Adadin ainihin mutuwar COVID-19 na iya zama mafi girma, saboda ba zai haɗa da mutanen da suka mutu ba tare da yin gwaji ba - misali a gida, a gidajen kula da tsofaffi, da sauransu.
Bayanai na ɓangare daga Italiya sun gano cewa yawan mutuwar wuce haddi yayin annobar ya wuce adadin mutuwar COVID na hukuma da kashi 4-5x.
" Wata mai magana da yawun Cibiyoyin Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cututtuka na Amurka (CDC) ta yarda da cewa "Mun san cewa [yawan mutuwar da aka bayyana] rashin kimantawa ne", wata sanarwa da rahotanni na rashin kimantawa a Amurka suka tabbatar. Irin wannan rashin kimantawa yakan faru a cikin annoba, kamar cutar zazzabin H1N1 na aladu na shekarar 2009. An tabbatar da mutuwar farko a Wuhan a ranar 9 ga Janairu 2020. "
Mutuwa ta farko a wajen kasar Sin ta faru ne a ranar 1 ga watan Fabrairu a Philippines, kuma mutuwar farko a wajen Asiya ta faru ne a Faransa a ranar 14 ga watan Fabrairu.
Zuwa 28 ga watan Fabrairu, a wajen kasar Sin, an samu mutuwar mutane fiye da goma sha biyu a kowanne a Iran, Koriya ta Kudu, da Italiya.
Zuwa 13 ga Maris, sama da kasashe da yankuna arba'in sun ba da rahoton mutuwar, a duk nahiyoyi ban da Antarctica. Ana amfani da ma'auni da yawa don ƙididdige yawan mutuwar.
Wadannan lambobi sun bambanta ta yankuna da kuma tsawon lokaci, kuma ana rinjayarsu ne da yawan gwajin, ingancin tsarin kiwon lafiya, zaɓuɓɓukan magani, lokaci tun farkon barkewar cutar, da halaye na yawan jama'a kamar su shekaru, jinsi, da kuma lafiyar gaba ɗaya. Matsayin mutuwa zuwa yanayin yana nuna adadin mutuwar da aka raba da adadin waɗanda aka gano a cikin wani lokaci.
Dangane da kididdigar Jami'ar Johns Hopkins, yawan mutuwar duniya zuwa cutar ya kai 6.0% (97,039/1,617,204) a ranar 10 ga Afrilu 2020.
Adadin ya bambanta bisa ga yankin.
A China, kimantawa game da adadin mutuwar zuwa yanayin ya ragu daga 17.3% (ga waɗanda ke da bayyanar cututtuka 110 Janairu 2020) zuwa 0.7% (ga waɗanda ke da bayyanar cututtuka bayan 1 Fabrairu 2020). Sauran matakan sun haɗa da yawan mutuwar mutum (CFR), wanda ke nuna yawan mutanen da aka gano waɗanda suka mutu daga cutar, da kuma yawan mutuwar kamuwa da cuta (IFR), wanda ke nuna yawan masu kamuwa da cuta (wanda aka gano da wanda ba a gano ba) waɗanda suka mutu daga cutar.
Waɗannan ƙididdigar ba su da lokaci kuma suna bin takamaiman yawan jama'a daga kamuwa da cuta zuwa warwarewar shari'ar.
Masana kimiyya da yawa sun yi ƙoƙari su ƙididdige waɗannan adadi don takamaiman mutane.
Cibiyar Kula da Magunguna ta Jami'ar Oxford ta kiyasta cewa yawan mutuwar kamuwa da cutar a cikin annobar gaba ɗaya yana tsakanin 0.1% da 0.39%.
Kimanin sama na wannan zangon ya yi daidai da sakamakon gwajin bazuwar farko na COVID-19 a Jamus, da kuma nazarin kididdiga da ke nazarin tasirin gwajin akan ƙididdigar CFR.
Hukumar ta WHO ta tabbatar da cewa za a iya sarrafa annobar.
Ba a san lokacin da cutar za ta kai kololuwa ba kuma tsawon lokacin da za ta yi ba kuma zai iya bambanta dangane da wurin da ake ci gaba.
" Maciej Boni na Jami'ar Jihar Penn ya bayyana, ""A bar shi ba tare da kulawa ba, yawanci annobar cutar tana kwance sannan kuma ta fara raguwa lokacin da cutar ta ƙare daga masu masaukin da ke akwai. "
"Amma kusan ba zai yiwu a yi wani tunani mai ma'ana ba a yanzu game da lokacin da hakan zai kasance".
" Babban mai ba da shawara kan harkokin kiwon lafiya na gwamnatin China Zhong Nanshan ya yi jayayya cewa ""zai iya karewa a watan Yuni"" idan za a iya tattara dukkan kasashe don bin shawarar WHO kan matakan da za a dauka don dakatar da yaduwar cutar. "
"A ranar 17 ga watan Maris, Adam Kucharski na Makarantar Lafiya da Magungunan Yanayi ta London ya bayyana cewa SARS-CoV-2 ""zai ci gaba da yaduwa, mai yiwuwa na shekara daya ko biyu". "
"A cewar binciken kwalejin Imperial da Neil Ferguson ya jagoranta, za a bukaci nisantar jiki da sauran matakan "har sai an samu rigakafin (mai yiwuwa watanni 18 ko sama da haka) ".
"William Schaffner na Jami'ar Vanderbilt ya bayyana, ""Ina ganin ba zai yiwu ba cewa wannan coronavirusdomin yana da saukin yaduwazai ɓace gaba ɗaya"" kuma zai iya ""mai yiwuwa ya zama cutar yanayi, yana dawowa kowace shekara"". "
Rashin lafiyar dawowar zai dogara ne da rigakafin garken da kuma yawan canjin.
Alamun COVID-19 na iya zama marasa takamaiman kuma mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar na iya zama marasa alamun.
Alamun biyu da suka fi kowa sune zazzabi (88%) da busassun tari (68%).
Alamun da ba sa bayyana sosai sun hada da gajiya, samar da ƙura a cikin numfashi (flegm), rashin jin ƙanshi, rashin numfashi, ciwon tsoka da na haɗin gwiwa, ciwon makogwaro, ciwon kai, sanyi, amai, hawan jini, zawo, ko cyanosis. WHO ta ce kusan mutum ɗaya cikin shida ya kamu da rashin lafiya mai tsanani kuma yana da wahalar numfashi.
Cibiyoyin Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Amurka (CDC) sun lissafa alamun gaggawa kamar wahalar numfashi, ciwon kirji ko matsin lamba, rikicewar kwatsam, wahalar farkawa, da fuska ko lebe masu shuɗi; ana ba da shawarar kulawar likita nan da nan idan waɗannan alamun sun kasance. Ƙarin ci gaban cutar na iya haifar da mummunar ciwon huhu, ciwon numfashi mai tsanani, sepsis, girgizar jini da mutuwa.
Wasu daga cikin wadanda suka kamu da cutar na iya zama marasa alamun cutar, ba tare da wata alama ta asibiti ba amma tare da sakamakon gwajin da ke tabbatar da kamuwa da cutar, don haka masu bincike sun ba da shawara cewa ya kamata a kula da waɗanda ke da kusanci da mutanen da aka tabbatar da kamuwa da cutar sosai kuma a bincika su don kawar da kamuwa da cuta.
Kimanin Sin na yawan marasa alamun cutar ya kasance daga kadan zuwa 44%.
Lokacin hawan da aka saba (lokacin tsakanin kamuwa da cuta da bayyanar cututtuka) ya kasance daga kwana daya zuwa 14, yawanci kwana biyar. A matsayin misali na rashin tabbas, kimantawa na kashi na mutanen da ke da COVID-19 waɗanda suka rasa ƙanshin su ya kasance 30% da farko kuma daga baya ya ragu zuwa 15%.
Har yanzu ana tantance wasu bayanai game da yadda cutar ke yaduwa.
An yi imanin cewa cutar tana yaduwa ne a lokacin kusanci da kuma ta ƙananan ɗigon ruwa da aka samar yayin tari, tari, ko magana; tare da kusanci na kusa da mita 1 zuwa 2 (3 zuwa 6 feet).
Nazarin ya gano cewa tari da ba a rufe ba na iya haifar da ɗigon ruwa da ke tafiya har zuwa mita 4.5 (15 feet) zuwa mita 8.2 (27 feet).
Wasu sun ba da shawarar cewa za a iya watsa kwayar ta ƙananan ɗigon ruwa waɗanda ke kasancewa na dogon lokaci a cikin iska, wanda za a iya samarwa yayin magana. Hakanan za a iya samar da ɗigon numfashi yayin numfashi, gami da lokacin magana, kodayake kwayar ba ta da iska.
Rashin ruwan zai iya sauka a bakin ko hanci na mutanen da ke kusa ko kuma a iya sha shi cikin huhu.
Wasu hanyoyin kiwon lafiya kamar su intuba da kuma sake farfadowa na zuciya da huhu (CPR) na iya haifar da ɓarkewar numfashi a cikin iska kuma don haka ya haifar da yaduwar iska.
Hakanan zai iya yaduwa idan mutum ya taɓa wani abu da ya ƙazantu, har da fata, sannan ya taɓa idanunsa, hanci, ko bakinsa.
Duk da cewa akwai damuwa cewa zai iya yaduwa ta hanyar kwance, ana ganin wannan hadarin yana da ƙaranci.
Gwamnatin China ta musanta yiwuwar watsa SARS-CoV-2 ta hanyar kwance-kwance. Kwayar cutar tana da saurin yaduwa a cikin kwanaki uku na farko bayan bayyanar cututtuka, kodayake yaduwa na iya yiwuwa kafin bayyanar cututtuka da kuma a cikin matakan cutar.
Mutane sun gwada tabbatacce ga cutar har zuwa kwanaki uku kafin bayyanar cututtuka yana nuna yiwuwar watsawa kafin ci gaba da bayyanar cututtuka masu mahimmanci.
Rahotanni kaɗan ne kawai na lab-tabbatar da marasa alamun cutar, amma wasu ƙasashe sun gano watsawar marasa alamun cutar yayin binciken gano lamba.
Cibiyar rigakafin cututtuka da kula da cuta ta Turai (ECDC) ta ce ko da yake ba a bayyana yadda cutar ke yaduwa cikin sauƙi ba, mutum ɗaya yawanci yana cutar da mutane biyu zuwa uku. Kwayar cutar tana rayuwa na tsawon sa'o'i zuwa kwanaki a kan farfajiyar jiki.
Musamman, an gano cewa cutar tana iya ganowa har tsawon kwanaki uku akan filastik (polypropylene) da bakin karfe 304, har tsawon rana daya akan kwali, da kuma har tsawon awanni huɗu akan jan karfe.
Wannan, duk da haka, ya bambanta dangane da zafi da zafin jiki. Dabbobi da sauran dabbobi sun gwada tabbatacce ga COVID-19.
Babu wata shaida da ta nuna cewa dabbobi na iya yada cutar zuwa ga mutane, duk da cewa hukumomin Birtaniya sun shawarci wanke hannu bayan sun yi hulda da dabbobi, kamar bayan sun yi hulda da wasu wuraren da mutane masu kamuwa da cutar suka taɓa.
Cutar coronavirus mai tsanani na numfashi mai tsanani 2 (SARS-CoV-2) wani sabon kwayar cuta ne, wanda aka fara warewa daga mutane uku da ke da ciwon huhu da ke da alaƙa da tarin cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani a Wuhan.
Dukkanin fasalulluka na sabon kwayar SARS-CoV-2 suna faruwa ne a cikin kwayar cutar corona da ke da alaƙa da juna a yanayi. A wajen jikin mutum, ana kashe kwayar cutar ta sabulu na gida, wanda ke narkar da murfin kariya. SARS-CoV-2 yana da alaƙa da SARS-CoV na asali.
Ana tunanin cewa yana da asalin zoonotic.
Binciken kwayoyin halitta ya bayyana cewa kwayar cutar coronavirus ta haɗu da nau'in Betacoronavirus, a cikin ƙaramin nau'in Sarbecovirus (tsarin B) tare da nau'ikan nau'ikan bat biyu.
Ya yi daidai da kashi 96% a matakin dukkanin kwayoyin halitta da sauran samfuran coronavirus na bat (BatCov RaTG13).
A watan Fabrairun 2020, masu binciken kasar Sin sun gano cewa akwai bambanci guda daya kawai na amino acid a wasu sassan jerin kwayoyin halittar tsakanin ƙwayoyin cuta daga pangolins da waɗanda daga mutane.
Kwatantawar dukkanin kwayoyin halitta ya zuwa yanzu ya gano a mafi yawan kashi 92% na kayan halittar da aka raba tsakanin pangolin coronavirus da SARS-CoV-2, wanda bai isa ya tabbatar da pangolins su zama mai masaukin baki ba.
Ana iya tantance kamuwa da kwayar cutar a wucin gadi bisa ga alamun, kodayake tabbatarwa a ƙarshe ta hanyar jujjuyawar juzu'in polymerase (rRT-PCR) na ɓoyayyen ɓoyayyen ƙwayar cuta ko CT.
Wani bincike da ya kwatanta PCR da CT a Wuhan ya nuna cewa CT ya fi PCR hankali, kodayake ba shi da takamaiman bayani, tare da yawancin fasalulluka na hoton da ke rufewa da sauran cututtukan huhu da kuma hanyoyin cutar.
"A watan Maris na shekarar 2020, Kwalejin Radiology ta Amurka ta ba da shawarar cewa ""kada a yi amfani da CT don tantancewa ko a matsayin gwajin farko don gano COVID-19". "
