An kuma shafi jadawalin jiragen sama kuma saboda haka an canza su. Koriya ta Kudu ta gabatar da abin da aka ɗauka shine mafi girma kuma mafi kyawun tsari a duniya don bincika yawan jama'a don cutar, da ware duk wani mutum da ya kamu da cutar da kuma ganowa da keɓe waɗanda suka tuntube su.
Hanyoyin tantancewa sun haɗa da tilastawa masu shigowa daga ƙasashen waje su ba da rahoton alamun cutar ta hanyar aikace-aikacen wayar hannu, gwajin cutar ta hanyar tuki tare da sakamakon da ake samu washegari, da kuma ƙara ƙarfin gwajin don ba da damar har zuwa mutane 20,000 a gwada kowace rana.
