Iran ta ba da rahoton farkon tabbatar da cutar SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 19 ga Fabrairu a Qom, inda, a cewar Ma'aikatar Lafiya da Ilimin Likita, mutane biyu suka mutu daga baya a wannan ranar.
Matakan farko da gwamnati ta sanar sun hada da soke kide kide da sauran al'amuran al'adu, wasannin motsa jiki, da sallar Juma'a, da rufe jami'o'i, cibiyoyin ilimi mafi girma, da makarantu.
Iran ta ware tiriliyan biyar na riyal don yaki da cutar.
Shugaba Hassan Rouhani ya ce a ranar 26 ga Fabrairu 2020 cewa babu wani shiri na killace yankunan da cutar ta shafa, kuma mutane ne kawai za a killace su.
An sanar da tsare-tsaren iyakance tafiye-tafiye tsakanin birane a watan Maris, kodayake ana ci gaba da zirga-zirgar ababen hawa tsakanin birane kafin Sabuwar Shekarar Farisa ta Nowruz.
An bude wuraren ibada na Shia a Qom ga mahajjata har zuwa 16 ga Maris 2020. Iran ta zama cibiyar yaduwar cutar bayan China a watan Fabrairu.
A tsakanin ikirarin rufewa game da yaduwar cutar a Iran, sama da kasashe goma sun gano yanayin su zuwa Iran a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, wanda ke nuna cewa yaduwar cutar na iya zama mafi tsanani fiye da 388 da gwamnatin Iran ta ruwaito a wannan ranar.
An rufe majalisar dokokin Iran, tare da 23 daga cikin mambobinta 290 da aka ruwaito sun gwada tabbatacce ga kwayar cutar a ranar 3 ga Maris.
A ranar 12 ga watan Maris, Human Rights Watch ta bukaci hukumomin gidan yari na Iran da su saki masu kare hakkin dan adam da aka tsare saboda rashin amincewarsu ta lumana, da kuma sake duk fursunonin da suka cancanci hakan.
Ya bayyana cewa akwai babban haɗarin yaduwar kwayar cutar a cikin rufe cibiyoyi kamar cibiyoyin tsare, waɗanda kuma ba su da isasshen kulawa ta likita.
