Gwajin RT-PCR da aka yi tare da swabs na makogwaro abin dogaro ne kawai a makon farko na cutar.
Daga baya kwayar cutar na iya bacewa a cikin makogwaro yayin da take ci gaba da ninka a cikin huhu.
Ga mutanen da suka kamu da cutar da aka gwada a mako na biyu, a madadin haka za a iya ɗaukar samfurin abu daga cikin hanyoyin numfashi mai zurfi ta hanyar tsotsa ko kuma za a iya amfani da kayan tari (spatum).
An haɓaka ɗayan farkon gwajin PCR a Charité a Berlin a cikin Janairu 2020 ta amfani da ainihin lokacin jujjuyawar juzu'in polymerase (rRT-PCR), kuma ya zama tushen kayan aikin 250,000 don rarraba ta Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO).
