b' Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) wani enzyme ne da ke haɗe da waje (cell membranes) na ƙwayoyin cikin huhu, jijiyoyi, zuciya, koda, da hanji.
ACE2 yana magance aikin enzyme mai canza angiotensin (ACE) ta hanyar rage adadin angiotensin-II da haɓaka Ang (((1-7) yana mai da shi kyakkyawan maƙasudin magani don magance cututtukan zuciya. ACE2 kuma yana aiki a matsayin hanyar shiga cikin ƙwayoyin wasu ƙwayoyin cuta.
Siffar ɗan adam na enzyme galibi ana kiranta da hACE2.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 wani zinc ne mai dauke da metalloenzyme da ke kan farfajiyar endothelial da sauran kwayoyin.
Kwayar ACE2 tana dauke da yankin N-terminal peptidase M2 da kuma yankin C-terminal collectrin na jigilar amino acid na koda.
ACE2 shine furotin mai wucewa guda ɗaya na nau'in I, tare da yankin da ke aiki da enzymatically wanda aka fallasa a farfajiyar ƙwayoyin a cikin huhu da sauran ƙwayoyin.
Ana raba yankin waje da kwayar halitta na ACE2 daga yankin transmembrane ta wani enzyme da aka sani da sheddase, kuma ana sakin furotin mai narkewa a cikin jini kuma a ƙarshe a fitar da shi cikin fitsari.
ACE2 yana nan a yawancin gabobin jiki: ACE2 yana haɗe da membrane na tantanin halitta na ƙwayoyin alveolar na nau'in huhu na II, enterocytes na ƙananan hanji, ƙwayoyin endothelial na jijiya da na jijiya da ƙwayoyin tsoka mai santsi na jijiya a yawancin gabobin jiki.
Hakanan ana samun bayyanar ACE2 mRNA a cikin kwakwalwar kwakwalwa, striatum, hypothalamus, da ƙwaƙwalwar kwakwalwa.
Babban aikin ACE2 shine yin aiki azaman ma'auni ga ACE.
ACE yana rarraba hormone na angiotensin I zuwa angiotensin II mai saurin saurin.
ACE2 a bayansa yana raba carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine daga angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) kuma yana hydrolyses shi cikin angiotensin mai fadada jijiya (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 kuma na iya rarraba wasu peptides da yawa ciki har da [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, da ghrelin.
ACE2 kuma yana daidaita safarar membrane na mai jigilar amino acid mai tsaka tsaki SLC6A19 kuma an haɗa shi da cutar Hartnup.
A matsayin furotin mai wucewa, ACE2 yana aiki a matsayin babban hanyar shiga cikin ƙwayoyin cuta don wasu ƙwayoyin cuta, gami da HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (kwayar cutar da ke haifar da SARS); da SARS-CoV-2 (kwayar cutar da ke haifar da COVID-19).
Musamman, haɗuwa da furotin S1 na SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV2 zuwa yankin enzymatic na ACE2 a saman ƙwayoyin yana haifar da endocytosis da sauyawar cutar da enzyme a cikin endosomes da ke cikin ƙwayoyin.
Wannan tsarin shigarwa kuma yana buƙatar ƙaddamar da furotin S ta mai masaukin baki serine protease TMPRSS2, wanda hanawa a halin yanzu yana ƙarƙashin bincike azaman mai yuwuwar magani. Wannan ya haifar da wasu suyi tunanin cewa rage matakan ACE2, a cikin ƙwayoyin, na iya taimakawa wajen yaƙar kamuwa da cuta.
Koyaya, ƙungiyoyi da yawa na ƙwararru da hukumomin kulawa sun ba da shawarar ci gaba da maganin ACE mai hanawa da ARB.
