Ana tsammanin ACE2 na mutum mai haɗuwa (rhACE2) shine sabon magani don raunin huhu mai tsanani, kuma ya bayyana don inganta hawan jini na huhu da ƙoshin oxygen a cikin aladu tare da lipopolysaccharide-induced acute respiratory distress syndrome.
Rabin rayuwar rhACE2 a cikin mutane kusan awanni 10 ne kuma farkon aiki mintuna 30 ne ban da tsawon lokacin aiki (tsawon) awanni 24.
Abubuwa da yawa sun nuna cewa rhACE2 na iya zama magani mai kyau ga waɗanda ke da rashin haƙuri ga masu hana tsarin renin-angiotensin na gargajiya (RAS inhibitors) ko kuma a cikin cututtuka inda ake yawan zagayawar angiotensin II. An kimanta rhACE2 da aka saka a cikin gwaji na asibiti don maganin cututtukan cututtukan numfashi.
