Bayanai na farko sun nuna cewa ana buƙatar manyan allurai na ribavirin don hana SARS-CoV-2 in vitro.
An ba da shawarar yin ƙarin nazarin in vivo na Nitazoxanide bayan nuna ƙarancin hana SARS-CoV-2. Nazarin ya nuna cewa farkon farawa na furotin mai ƙwanƙwasa ta hanyar transmembrane protease serine 2 (TMPRSS2) yana da mahimmanci don shigar da SARS-CoV-2 ta hanyar hulɗa tare da mai karɓar ACE2.
Nazarin chloroquine da hydroxychloroquine tare da ko ba tare da azithromycin ba suna da manyan iyakoki waɗanda suka hana ƙungiyar likitanci rungumar waɗannan hanyoyin magani ba tare da ƙarin bincike ba. Oseltamivir baya hana SARS-CoV-2 in vitro kuma ba shi da sanannen rawa a cikin maganin COVID-19.
Cytokine storm na iya zama rikitarwa a cikin matakan ƙarshe na COVID-19 mai tsanani.
Akwai shaidar cewa hydroxychloroquine na iya samun kaddarorin anti-cytokine storm. Tocilizumab an haɗa shi cikin jagororin magani ta Hukumar Lafiya ta China bayan an kammala karamin bincike.
Ana gudanar da gwajin kashi na 2 wanda ba a yi amfani da shi ba a matakin kasa a Italiya bayan nuna sakamako mai kyau a cikin mutane masu cutar mai tsanani.
A hade tare da gwajin jini na ferritin na jini don gano guguwar cytokine, an yi nufin magance irin waɗannan ci gaba, wanda ake tsammanin shine dalilin mutuwa a wasu mutanen da ke fama da cutar.
FDA ta amince da mai adawa da mai karɓar interleukin-6 bisa nazarin yanayin baya don maganin cutar cutar cytokine mai hana steroid wanda ya haifar da wani dalili daban, maganin kwayoyin CAR T, a cikin 2017.
Ya zuwa yanzu, babu wata hujja da aka yi ta bazuwar, da aka sarrafa cewa tocilizumab magani ne mai inganci ga CRS.
Ana binciken canja wurin tsarkakewa da kuma tsananin ƙwayoyin cuta da tsarin rigakafin waɗanda suka warke daga COVID-19 ke samarwa ga mutanen da suke buƙatar su a matsayin hanyar da ba rigakafin rigakafi ba.
An gwada wannan dabarar don SARS tare da sakamako mara tabbatacce.
Rashin tasirin kwayar cuta shine tsarin aiki da ake tsammani wanda maganin rigakafin jiki na iya shiga tsakani a cikin kariya daga SARS-CoV-2.
Sauran hanyoyin, kamar su cytotoxicity na tantanin halitta da ke dogara da antibody da/ ko phagocytosis, na iya yiwuwa.
Sauran nau'ikan maganin rigakafin rigakafi, misali, ta amfani da samfuran rigakafin monoclonal, suna cikin ci gaba.
Za a iya ƙara samar da maganin magani na mai warkarwa, wanda ya ƙunshi ruwan jini daga marasa lafiya da suka warke kuma ya ƙunshi ƙwayoyin cuta na musamman ga wannan kwayar, don saurin saurin.
